241
00:18:15,323 --> 00:18:16,908
Pero hinahanap namin kung saan-saan.

242
00:18:17,158 --> 00:18:18,451
Dapat ay mayroon tayong magandang balita sa lalong madaling panahon.

243
00:18:18,660 --> 00:18:19,661
Sige.

244
00:18:22,831 --> 00:18:24,499
Sinabi mismo ng Panginoon.

245
00:18:25,583 --> 00:18:27,585
"Kumatok ka, at ang pinto ay bubuksan."

246
00:18:28,002 --> 00:18:29,546
Kaya kumatok. Kumatok hanggang sa ito ay magbukas.

247
00:18:29,629 --> 00:18:31,339
Kumatok! At huwag kang sumuko.

248
00:18:31,506 --> 00:18:32,507
Amen.

249
00:18:33,216 --> 00:18:35,802
JUMBO 24

250
00:18:42,434 --> 00:18:43,518
Seoraksan.

251
00:18:44,978 --> 00:18:46,896
Ang Seoraksan ay isang bundok
sa Lalawigan ng Gangwon.

252
00:18:47,105 --> 00:18:48,314
