- Sige.

264
00:19:15,467 --> 00:19:17,260
Handa na akong sumuko kahit papaano.

265
00:19:18,678 --> 00:19:19,721
Tingnan mo itong punk na ito.

266
00:19:20,013 --> 00:19:21,598
