267
00:19:21,765 --> 00:19:22,766
Malala na ang problema mo ngayon.

268
00:19:23,224 --> 00:19:24,684
Akala mo ikaw lang ang
may kakayahang maghubad ng isang bagay?

269
00:19:25,351 --> 00:19:26,519
