288
00:20:31,376 --> 00:20:32,377
Kung lagi mong sinasabing oo

289
00:20:32,460 --> 00:20:34,045
Ituturing ka nilang isang taong pabaya
at dadagdagan pa nila ang trabaho mo.

290
00:20:34,128 --> 00:20:35,129
Tama ka.

291
00:20:35,296 --> 00:20:37,507
Sige. Sa susunod, tatanggihan ko na nang diretso.

292
00:20:38,925 --> 00:20:39,926
Bilisan natin.

293
00:20:40,385 --> 00:20:41,386
Tagapamahala Bong.

294
00:20:42,470 --> 00:20:43,763
Pasensya na...

295
00:20:44,764 --> 00:20:46,307
pero medyo busy ako ngayon.

296
00:20:49,018 --> 00:20:50,395
Tama ba ang narinig ko?

297
00:20:53,189 --> 00:20:54,190
Busy ka?

298
00:20:59,612 --> 00:21:01,614
Kahit busy ka,
kailangan kitang hugasan ang kotse ko.

299
00:21:02,031 --> 00:21:03,032
Siguraduhing walang bahid ito.

300
00:21:13,668 --> 00:21:14,669
Magandang pitch!

301
00:21:16,337 --> 00:21:17,338
Boss.

302
00:21:27,140 --> 00:21:28,433
