330
00:23:06,072 --> 00:23:08,116
Teka, bakit kayo lang
ng biyenan ko?

331
00:23:08,616 --> 00:23:09,617
Nasaan ang nanay ni Ji-woo?

332
00:23:09,784 --> 00:23:11,869
Sabi niya may meeting daw siya sa dance club.

333
00:23:11,953 --> 00:23:13,037
